      </h2>
      <p>
        {i18n.PAGES.PRIVACY.LINKS.DESCRIPTION_1}
      </p>
      <p>
        {i18n.PAGES.PRIVACY.LINKS.DESCRIPTION_2}
      </p>
      <h2 class=`${H2_STYLES}`>
        {i18n.PAGES.PRIVACY.RIGHT_OF_EXCLUSION.TITLE}
      </h2>
      <p><>
        {i18n.PAGES.PRIVACY.RIGHT_OF_EXCLUSION.DESCRIPTION_1}
